            <lg xml:id="TK1298">
<l>eḷḷi ṉiḷivāmeṉ ṟeṇṇi yavartiṟa </l>
<l>muḷḷu muyirkkāta ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My soul which clings to life thinks only of his (own) gain in the belief that it would be disgraceful for it to despise him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
